}

###

# @name Update post content and status
# @description Update multiple fields at once
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/posts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Updated content with more details.",
  "status": "published"
}

###

# =============================================================================
# Delete Post
# =============================================================================

###
# @name Delete a post
